```swift
class CustomGroupChannelViewController: SBUGroupChannelViewController {
    override func baseChannelModule(_ listComponent: SBUBaseChannelModule.List, fullMessagesInTableView tableView: UITableView) -> [BaseMessage] {
        let messageList = super.baseChannelModule(listComponent, fullMessagesInTableView: tableView)
        
        let enabled = messageList.filter({ $0 is UserMessage }).count > 2
        (self.baseInputComponent?.messageInputView as? SBUMessageInputView)?.setInputState(enabled, placeholder: "please select suggested replies.")
        
        return messageList
    }
}

```
